### ══════════════════════════════════════════
###  M4 API TESTS  — Use with VS Code REST Client
###  or paste URLs into Postman / Insomnia
### ══════════════════════════════════════════


### ─────────────────────────────────────────
###  ALUMNI  —  /alumni
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### 1. Add Carol Lee (mentorship OPEN)
POST http://localhost:5000/alumni
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Carol Lee",
  "email": "carol@example.com",
  "graduationYear": 2022,
  "currentCompany": "Google",
  "jobTitle": "Software Engineer II",
  "lpa": 45,
  "cgpa": 9.2,
  "branch": "CSE",
  "skills": ["Java", "System Design", "Kotlin"],
  "linkedin": "https://linkedin.com/in/carollee",
  "github": "https://github.com/carollee",
  "bio": "Focus on DSA early. Internships are gold.",
  "mentorshipOpen": true
}

###

### 2. Add David Kim (mentorship CLOSED)
POST http://localhost:5000/alumni
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "David Kim",
  "email": "david@example.com",
  "graduationYear": 2021,
  "currentCompany": "Microsoft",
  "jobTitle": "Senior SDE",
  "lpa": 52,
  "cgpa": 8.9,
  "branch": "IT",
  "skills": ["C#", ".NET", "Azure"],
  "linkedin": "https://linkedin.com/in/davidkim",
  "bio": "Open source contributions open doors.",
  "mentorshipOpen": false
}

###

### 3. Get all alumni
GET http://localhost:5000/alumni

###

### 4. Get single alumni (replace ID)
GET http://localhost:5000/alumni/<ALUMNI_ID_HERE>

###

### 5. Update alumni — change job title
PUT http://localhost:5000/alumni/<ALUMNI_ID_HERE>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jobTitle": "Staff Engineer",
  "lpa": 60,
  "mentorshipOpen": true
}

###

### 6. Toggle mentorship ON/OFF
PATCH http://localhost:5000/alumni/<ALUMNI_ID_HERE>/mentorship

###

### 7. Delete alumni (admin use)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/alumni/<ALUMNI_ID_HERE>

###


### ─────────────────────────────────────────
###  MENTORSHIP  —  /mentorship
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### 8. Student sends mentorship request
###    (replace studentId and alumniId with real Firestore IDs)
POST http://localhost:5000/mentorship
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "<STUDENT_ID_HERE>",
  "studentName": "Alice Johnson",
  "alumniId": "<ALUMNI_ID_HERE>",
  "topic": "Cracking Google interviews",
  "message": "Hi Carol, I am a 3rd year CSE student preparing for product companies. I keep getting stuck at system design rounds. Would love your guidance on how you prepared and any resources you found helpful."
}

###

### 9. Get all mentorship requests (admin view)
GET http://localhost:5000/mentorship

###

### 10. Get requests FOR a specific alumni
GET http://localhost:5000/mentorship/alumni/<ALUMNI_ID_HERE>

###

### 11. Get requests BY a specific student
GET http://localhost:5000/mentorship/student/<STUDENT_ID_HERE>

###

### 12. Alumni ACCEPTS a request
PATCH http://localhost:5000/mentorship/<REQUEST_ID_HERE>/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "accepted",
  "scheduledAt": "2025-08-10T10:00:00.000Z",
  "notes": "Let us schedule a 30-min call via Google Meet."
}

###

### 13. Alumni DECLINES a request
PATCH http://localhost:5000/mentorship/<REQUEST_ID_HERE>/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "declined",
  "notes": "Currently too busy but try again next month."
}

###

### 14. Alumni marks session COMPLETED
PATCH http://localhost:5000/mentorship/<REQUEST_ID_HERE>/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "completed",
  "notes": "Had a great 45-min session. Covered system design basics."
}

###

### 15. Delete a request (admin use)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/mentorship/<REQUEST_ID_HERE>

###


### ─────────────────────────────────────────
###  EXTERNAL JOBS  —  /external
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### 16. Get all external jobs (seed data)
GET http://localhost:5000/external/jobs

###

### 17. Search for Python jobs
GET http://localhost:5000/external/jobs?q=python

###

### 18. Filter internships only
GET http://localhost:5000/external/jobs?type=internship

###

### 19. Filter LinkedIn full-time jobs
GET http://localhost:5000/external/jobs?source=linkedin&type=full-time

###

### 20. Search + filter combined
GET http://localhost:5000/external/jobs?q=react&type=internship&source=internshala

###


